{"title":"为罪魁招魂","authors":["池北偶","朱根华"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为罪魁招魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶 诗  朱根华 画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本右翼政客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个头脑发昏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀念当年霸业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘皇军功勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年参拜神社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘当孝子贤孙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想给战犯翻案，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为罪魁招魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤军国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心旧梦重温。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若走侵略老路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就步东条后尘。*"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切莫执迷不悟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"免得玩火自焚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*指落得与东条同样的下场。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}